      "name": "dark-editorial",
      "description": "AI-extracted template from reference design",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Design Conversion</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600&family=Ma+Shan+Zheng&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --bg: #0a0a0a;\n            --text: #f0f0f0;\n            --text-muted: #a0a0a0;\n            /* Not explicitly used in this design, but defined as per requirements */\n            --primary: transparent;\n            --secondary: transparent;\n            --accent: transparent;\n            --surface: transparent;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            background-color: #1a1a1a; /* A slightly lighter background for the canvas itself to stand out */\n        }\n\n        .canvas {\n            width: 1080px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background-color: var(--bg);\n            color: var(--text);\n            font-family: 'Lora', serif;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            padding: 80px; /* Consistent padding around the edges */\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in width/height */\n        }\n\n        header {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: flex-start; /* Align items to the top */\n            margin-bottom: auto; /* Pushes main content down */\n            padding-bottom: 40px; /* Space between header and main content */\n        }\n\n        .header-left {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 4px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n\n        .header-right {\n            font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive; /* A calligraphic Chinese font */\n            font-size: 48px; /* Larger size for the stylized characters */\n            line-height: 1;\n            font-weight: 400;\n        }\n\n        main {\n            flex-grow: 1; /* Allows main content to take available space */\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */\n            align-items: center; /* Center vertically */\n            text-align: left; /* Text itself is left-aligned within its block */\n            padding: 0 100px; /* Add horizontal padding to main content area */\n        }\n\n        .body-text {\n            font-family: 'Lora', serif;\n            font-size: 40px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            max-width: 600px; /* Control line length */\n            margin: 0; /* Remove default paragraph margin */\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: flex-end; /* Align items to the bottom */\n            margin-top: auto; /* Pushes footer down */\n            padding-top: 40px; /* Space between main content and footer */\n        }\n\n        .footer-left,\n        .footer-right {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n        }\n        .footer-left p, .footer-right p {\n            margin: 0; /* Remove default paragraph margins */\n        }\n    </style>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"canvas\">\n        <header>\n            <div class=\"header-left\">{{brand_name}}</div>\n            <div class=\"header-right\">{{brand_name}}</div>\n        </header>\n\n        <main>\n            <p class=\"body-text\">{{body}}</p>\n        </main>\n\n        <footer>\n            <div class=\"footer-left\">\n                <p>Alan Hong</p>\n                <p>@thealanhong</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"footer-right\">\n                <p>\u00a9The Codexx 2026</p>\n                <p>www.thecodexx.com</p>\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n    <script>lucide.createIcons()</script>\n</body>\n</html>",
